00:03:17.890 --> 00:03:19.840 align:middle line:90%
reversible brain changes.

00:03:19.840 --> 00:03:23.080 align:middle line:84%
The pain is a sort
of a false alarm.

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:27.850 align:middle line:84%
