00:03:31.510 --> 00:03:33.140 align:middle line:90%
the state of the body.

00:03:33.140 --> 00:03:37.960 align:middle line:84%
The second piece of PRT is
learning to feel differently

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:40.720 align:middle line:84%
